EBK13.original: I can't give you any more of the information you want. I am emailing my contacts in the Caspian and keep getting reports that the addresses no longer exist. Also, the companies you want info on seem to be owned by umbrella corporations which are owned by even more umbrella corporations. Tracing the money I reach dead ends in either the Caymans or Switzerland.
EBK13.translated: 没法为你提供更进一步的情报了。我正在联系里海那边的线人，但收到的答复一直是地址不存在。还有，你让我调查的公司似乎有多家马甲母公司，这些马甲母公司又有更多家马甲母公司。对资金流动的调查最终都在开曼群岛和瑞士走入了死胡同。

EBK13.original: Sorry I cannot help you further.
EBK13.translated: 对不起，只能帮到这里了。
